On Monday, six Bay Area counties announced shelter in place orders will be enacted starting at midnight.
Here's what you need to know about the shelter in place orders:How long does it last?
"These measure will be disruptive to day-to-day life, but there is no need to panic," San Francisco Mayor London Breed said.